		<title>就是不肯認錯！貓咪搗蛋被抓包卻「理直氣壯」讓主人超無奈 </title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/30/%e5%b0%b1%e6%98%af%e4%b8%8d%e8%82%af%e8%aa%8d%e9%8c%af%ef%bc%81%e8%b2%93%e5%92%aa%e6%90%97%e8%9b%8b%e8%a2%ab%e6%8a%93%e5%8c%85%e5%8d%bb%e3%80%8c%e7%90%86%e7%9b%b4%e6%b0%a3%e5%a3%af%e3%80%8d%e8%ae%93/</link>
		
